{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/TakeBackOurPlanet_Header.png?t=1726755768\" /><br>An experiment gone wrong unleashed a relentless alien invasion, plunging humanity into chaos. Price Inc. initiated the <strong>BIG SHOTS</strong> Initiative to fight the invaders; this is where you come in, rookie. Become a Big Shot and take on the pivotal role of an alien exterminator. As you gear up and evolve your mech, you\u2019ll venture deeper into infested areas in search of the source of all this mayhem.<br>  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/TakeBackOurPlanet_Header.gif?t=1726755768\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/SoloOrCo-op_Header.png?t=1726755768\" /><br>Exterminations can be done solo or side by side with a fellow big shot. When teamed up, working together is key to holding off alien scum and getting the job done. Cross-platform play is supported, so none of your friends will be left out!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/SoloOrCoOp.gif?t=1726755768\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/BuildYourMech_Header.png?t=1726755768\" /><br>Evolve your humble mech with upgrades during runs, becoming the ultimate alien exterminator in your crazy rogue-lite adventure. Explore the possibilities and combinations from the upgrades presented to you, or change your loadout with the permanent upgrades that you can acquire in the shop back at the hangar!<br>   <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/BuildYourMech_Gif.gif?t=1726755768\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/UnlimitedMobility_Header.png?t=1726755768\" /><br>BIG SHOTS\u00ae is a fresh take on the popular wave shooter &amp; roguelite genre in virtual reality. Take advantage of our innovative movement system to move around freely in a swift, immersive, and comfortable manner. No more standing in predefined positions or being restricted by teleportation, but unlimited mobility and opportunities at your disposal.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666530/extras/Unlimited_Mobility.gif?t=1726755768\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fashionista!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/9090ff40ed1ff72ca95fabc40fe9311483cd6d67.jpg"},{"name":"Mechlander","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/cedf4f2ea40bb7a99f719ef438564436e326e852.jpg"},{"name":"Conqueror of All Maps!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/428e36321046d53ec21983989a74d2100e412076.jpg"},{"name":"Big Shot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/89493a20e7e3bed81b0794d6e18ae7ed736e2cad.jpg"},{"name":"Thanks for watching!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/2757771042d21ae59567fe354aa2e8702481d649.jpg"},{"name":"Mine, mine, MINEEEEEE!!!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/10301537b7030bfa7434a3c2e38618953bc3e7f8.jpg"},{"name":"Slimy yet satisfying.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/39ce59a22d42d1fd7da422181bc4a07e0aa4463e.jpg"},{"name":"Maxed out and ready to rumble!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666530/4bb71f1f96566cf093478ea707c0d1e9dd3039e2.jpg"},{"name":"Repurposed Bug parts","path":"https://c